data.description: A Beautiful Single Family Home with 3 Bedrooms and 2 baths located in a nice neighborhood in the City of Lancaster.  This is  great opportunity to own a spacious and well maintained single family home with hardwood floors and tiles all over the house with a huge permitted Bonus Room. Owner passed away in the property, natural Death  This is a must see property.
